additionalNotes: The Warfighter 7.62 MM Garrison Rosado is a medium strength cigar that is hand rolled by Plasencia Cigars. Its dark, oily Nicaraguan Habano maduro wrapper covers a Nicaraguan Habano binder, and a blended filler made of Dominican Republic and Nicaraguan Habano tobaccos. The Warfighter 7.62 MM Garrison Rosado is a spicy stick with notes of wood, floral, and coffee.
